body:
#### PR description:

- Remaining header files in src/ were moved to interface/
- Very old CSC cabling maps in python/ were removed
- Configurations in test/ were consolidated into `testCSCDigi2Raw_cfg.py` for Run-3
- Old doc/ file was deleted
- Header guards according to CMS style

#### PR validation:

Code compiles

N/A

FYI @ptcox, @barvic: after this PR we should start putting in the pieces for the GEM data and Run-3 CSC CLCTs and LCTs.
title: Clean up CSCRawToDigi for Run-3
